-- Novak Djokovic Beats Andy Roddick at Olympic Tennis Tournament
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-07-31T16:20:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-31/novak-djokovic-beats-andy-roddick-at-olympic-tennis-tournament.html
World No. 2 Novak Djokovic of Serbia
beat  Andy Roddick  of the U.S. 6-2, 6-1 at Wimbledon to reach the
third round of the Olympic tennis tournament.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
